description: The fund is an actively managed ETF that seeks capital appreciation by gaining exposure to the global carbon credit market. The fund invests in carbon credit futures contracts, which are commodity futures contracts linked to the value of emission allowances. The fund also may invest in (i) ETFs that provide exposure to government or investment grade corporate fixed income securities with maturities up to 12 months; (ii) money market funds; and (iii) cash and cash equivalents. It is non-diversified.
name: Carbon Strategy ETF
